<#
.SYNOPSIS
    This PowerShell script ensures that the maximum size of the Windows Application event log is at least 32768 KB (32 MB).

.NOTES
    Author          : Yamen Rashwani
    LinkedIn        : www.linkedin.com/in/yamen-rashwani-90260b2a7
    GitHub          : https://github.com/Rashwani/Yamen-Rashwani
    Date Created    : 2026-04-03
    Last Modified   : 2026-04-03
    Version         : 1.0
    CVEs            : N/A
    Plugin IDs      : N/A
    STIG-ID         : WN11-AU-000500

.TESTED ON
    Date(s) Tested  : 
    Tested By       : 
    Systems Tested  : 
    PowerShell Ver. : 

.USAGE
    Put any usage instructions here.
    Example syntax:
    PS C:\> .\(STIG-ID-WN11-AU-000500).ps1 
#>

# YOUR CODE GOES HERE

New-Item -Path "HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\EventLog\Application" -Force | Out-Null

Set-ItemProperty -Path "HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\EventLog\Application" `
  -Name "MaxSize" -Value 32768 -Type DWord
